Package org.jets3t.apps.cockpit Description

Provides Cockpit, a graphical Java application for viewing and managing the contents of an Amazon S3 account.

Cockpit can be run as a stand-alone application or deployed as an applet.

Related Documentation

For more information and help please see the Cockpit Guide.
